Câu lệnh hay dùng cơ bản

mysql -h 94.237.60.55 -P 33502 -u root -p
show databases;
USE school;    dùng table school 
DESCRIBE students;  // xem cấu trúc của table 
SHOW COLUMNS FROM students;
SELECT * FROM students LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM students WHERE student_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM ten_bang WHERE name LIKE 'Bar%';




                    +-----------------+
                    |  SQL Injections |
                    +-----------------+
                       /      |       \
                      /       |        \
                     /        |         \
          +---------+   +-----+-----+    +-------------+
          | In-band |   |   Blind    |    | Out-of-band|
          +---------+   +-----------+    +-------------+
           /     \         /      \
          /       \       /        \
 +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+
 | Union Based   | | Error Based   | | Boolean Based | | Time Based    |
 +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+




Query:
SELECT * FROM logins 
WHERE username='admin' OR '1'='1' AND password='something'

Biểu diễn logic:
   username='admin'  ---> True
                               \
                                OR ----> True
                               /
        '1'='1' ---> True ----AND----> False (password='something' sai)
                                   \
                                    False
